To control how much the ball-speed increases when
hitting a brick in this level, use the > inc FLOAT command
> inc 0.003
will make the ball-speed increase by 0.003 glunits pr brick it hits, this is the standard for normal difficulty.
This value is ignored by "easy" difficulty

> down 10000
